Black develops his last piece while still possible. The b7 pawn is en prise. 18. Qxb7 Rxf1+, 19. Kxf1 Rf8+, 20. Ke2 Ne7, 21. Qxa7 Bb6 was definitely playable. But the mission is to capture the King, not eliminate minions. Anything less would not be quite as beautiful.
